data.description: This 3 bed 3 bath home conveniently located within minutes of major highways is ready for its new owners! The main floor features a spacious living room, a breakfast room with a beautiful brick fireplace, a large kitchen with granite countertops & granite backsplash, as well as 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Head downstairs to find a large rec room with a wet bar, a bonus room, a half bath/laundry room, and plenty of storage space. Walk out back and find your large fully fenced in backyard with a newly stained deck that’s great for entertaining! Property is being sold as-is.
